snippet.title: Birth of Cultures - 4X Strategy Game - Reveal Teaser
snippet.description:
BoC is a historical 4X strategy game. Play on diverse planets with climate simulation and non-linear progression over the last 60,000 years of human evolution. Develop your own ancient civilization starting as a nomadic tribe from the last Ice Age.

Wishlist on Steam:
http://steam.camlanngames.com/?appId=1159150
